          <h4>Iteration &amp; Implementation</h4>
        <div class="left-zeit">
          <p>In two days we were able to outline the concerns or questions users had so that we could continue improving the overall experience.</p>
          <p>I started looking at how other brands were communicating with users as inspiration for how we could make Zeit more approachable.</p>
          <p>I made iterations that focused on using natural language to build trust with even the most skeptical users, and present it to them in a very readable format. These little iterations provided the mechanism for users to dig deeper into understanding how to book time-travel online. </p>
            <img src="images/mandela.jpg">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

