      <div class="column">
          <h2>Next Steps</h2>
        <div class="left-zeit">
          <p>Building an intuitive and tasteful digital product is one of the most exciting things for a designer. In our case, it is not only about providing a useful tool for travelers, but it’s also about having positive strategic results for the business. </p>
          <p>Our first step is to continue performing usability tests, collecting insight from our users, and starting to develop more integrations. We'll be able to test these changes using a hi-fidelity prototype which would be our second go-to action after the usability tests.</p>
          <p>In conclusion, the more data that we have, the more opportunities we have to make that data useful. While we may expand our product scope, data-informed decisions will be ingrained within the fabric of Zeit.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
